hcc_text: Bruckner Boulevard is in the middle third in the Bronx for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile.
info: At Bruckner Boulevard at Bruckner Boulevard Wb, Bx River Parkway Sb Exit 2 West and Morrison Avenue, there were 11 injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
